---
import BaseLayout from "../../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro";
import { t } from "../../lib/i18n";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — James Lyu">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light tracking-tight text-ink mb-8">
      {t("en", "about.title")}
    </h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg text-muted leading-relaxed space-y-6">
      <p>
        {t("en", "about.content")}
      </p>
      <p>
        Photography, for me, is not just about the final image — it's about the
        moment of discovery. The way light falls on a quiet street at dusk, the
        geometry of shadows on a building facade, or the unguarded expression on
        a stranger's face. These are the moments I chase.
      </p>
      <p>
        This portfolio is a curated selection of my work across landscapes,
        street photography, architecture, and more. Each image tells a story of
        a place, a time, and a feeling.
      </p>
      <p>
        I shoot primarily with a Sony mirrorless system and have a deep
        appreciation for natural light and candid composition.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
